    "name": "F1717 Compression-Bending Verification Requirement",
    "description": "The FEA model's predictions of construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement shall be verified against physical hardware measurements obtained through a controlled experiment. The controlled experiment shall prescribe boundary conditions, crosshead displacement rate (5 mm/min ± 0.5 mm/min), specimen temperature (37 °C ± 1 °C), and UHMWPE block geometry in accordance with ASTM F1717-21 Section 8. Independent replication across at least two test operators is required to confirm repeatability before comparison with FEA outputs.",
    "requiredVerificationMethod": "controlled-experiment",
    "acceptanceCriteria": "All QoI predictions within 10% of mean experimental value; normalised error E/uval < 1.96 for each QoI."
