      "name": "Multi-site F1717 compression-bending observational validation — stiffness, yield force, 40 mm force",
      "description": "FEA predictions for construct stiffness (N/mm), yield force (N), and force at 40 mm displacement (N) were compared against bench-test records assembled from two independent laboratories (Lab A: n=6; Lab B: n=5). All three QoIs fell within the 10% acceptance bound; normalised errors were 0.83, 1.12, and 0.74 respectively, each below the 1.96 threshold. The multi-laboratory coverage and consistent instrumentation across sites provide strong corroborating evidence for model fidelity. Data were collected under standard operating procedures at each site; crosshead rate and specimen geometry were recorded as part of routine lab documentation rather than being prospectively controlled by the study team.",
